  ],
  "remarks": "Executive Director of the Tecmash concern. Tecmash is a key designer and manufacturer of missiles and munitions used by the Russian Armed Forces. Its subordinate company, NPO Splav, manufactures BM-27 Uragan and BM-30 Smerch multiple rocket launchers that were used by the Russian Armed Forces during Russia’s war of aggression against Ukraine. Russian Armed Forces employed BM-27 Uragan and BM-30 Smerch multiple rocket launchers in cluster munition strikes against civilian targets in Ukraine, that caused multiple casualties.",
